         <p style="line-height:24px;letter-spacing:0px; color:#4a4a4a; text-align:justify;list-style-position: inside"><img src="images/arrow.gif"/>10,034 people surveyed; 66% are from rural India while 34% are from urban India</p>
         <p style="line-height:24px;letter-spacing:0px; color:#4a4a4a; text-align:justify;list-style-position: inside"><img src="images/arrow.gif"/>Overall household spending up for 56%, highest from Telangana and Andhra Pradesh</p>
