         <img src="images/CSI-Sep22.jpg" style="width:50%; height:auto;;display: block; float:left;margin:5px 20px 4px 0" class="img-thumbnail">
         <p style="line-height:24px;letter-spacing:0px;color:#4a4a4a"><b><b>48% shop more during the festive season compared to rest of the year, as per Axis My India Sep CSI Survey.</b></b></p>
         <p style="line-height:24px;letter-spacing:0px; color:#4a4a4a; text-align:justify;list-style-position: inside"><img src="images/arrow.gif"/>  20% to shop more this festive season than last year.</p>
         <p style="line-height:24px;letter-spacing:0px; color:#4a4a4a; text-align:justify;list-style-position: inside"><img src="images/arrow.gif"/>  (A&M) 61% watch online video content like YouTube/OTT on their mobile/connected TV as per Axis My India Sep CSI Survey.</p>
         <p style="line-height:24px;letter-spacing:0px; color:#4a4a4a; text-align:justify;list-style-position: inside"><img src="images/arrow.gif"/>  Average 9 apps used by a smartphone user.</p>
         <p style="line-height:24px;letter-spacing:0px; color:#4a4a4a; text-align:justify;list-style-position: inside"><img src="images/arrow.gif"/>  10014 people surveyed 68% is from rural India while 32% is from urban India.</p>
         <p style="line-height:24px;letter-spacing:0px; color:#4a4a4a; text-align:justify;list-style-position: inside"><img src="images/arrow.gif"/>  Overall household spending has increased for 61%, net score at +53.</p>
